---
import '../styles/home.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#f3eddf" />
    <title>页面未找到 · Atthis</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main id="main" class="not-found">
      <p class="eyebrow">404 · SOURCE NOT DECLARED</p>
      <h1>这里没有这页内容</h1>
      <p>网站只投影已经声明的项目来源。你可以返回文档入口继续。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="primary-action" href="/docs/">返回文档 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        <a class="text-action" href="/">返回首页</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
